Metadata: Ocean and Coastal Law Memo (Issue 37, February 1991)
Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program
One issue of this newsletter received for 1991.

Ocean and Coastal Law Memo is an aperiodic publication of the University of Oregon Ocean and Coastal Law Center (OCLC) and is distributed by the Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program. The main topic in this issue is: Recent Developments in Ocean and Coastal Law, 1990, J. Kellerman.
